{"tid":758876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔怕得罪強國】越南准台商高掛台灣旗  免排華示威受攻擊","createTime":"2018-07-28T06:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T07:20:31.000Z","uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa12544374137e42a1ea1355a8f9a86b7602baf","tid":758876,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:09:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180728&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58496618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180728%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58496618&d=uBYLp38IdER8mI%2BiaMykeVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=a4d73cf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180728%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58496618&h=d5b19cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180728&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58496618</a><br />\n【唔怕得罪強國】越南准台商高掛台灣旗  免排華示威受攻擊"},{"pid":"933969579eaf8df23ebb26b406035a97064dae56","tid":758876,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"越南曾在2014年爆發大規模的「513排華事件」，雖然當時許多越南人衝着中國工廠抗議，但由於多數人分不清楚台灣廠商與中國廠商，導致不少台商也跟着遭殃。但現在有台商指出，越南政府為了辨別台商與中國廠商，同意台商廠區可高掛青天白日滿地紅旗。<br />\n<br />\n據中央社報道，在越南平陽開設家具廠、來自台灣的凱勝家具總裁羅子文表示，在爆發513排華事件後，公司的確受到了影響，損失約100萬美元（約780萬港元）。後來凱勝與越南政府交涉，越南政府除了給予一定金額抵稅作為補償，也提到民眾對於台灣和中國企業，常常傻傻分不清，才會誤砸台企廠房。之後越南政府同意，為了識別台灣企業，可以把台灣旗高高掛。<br />\n羅子文表示，以往掛台灣旗都會受到中國干預，向越南公安通報後都會被要求卸下，但現在是「光明正大把台灣的國旗每天都豎起來」。他更直呼這樣高掛台灣旗，「在以前是沒辦法做到的事」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed127dec2dda1cd1e8c579a01cd2489c6a735e8e","tid":758876,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍一百年後，黎次十六國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7cf70ed8cfef39b89741836655bb07787c52e8","tid":758876,"uid":32832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"200％肯定支那廠會掛台灣旗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b880dd8aec79cec45763bdf693e76e3186353a","tid":758876,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}